casebody.data:
No. 09-9225. Rodney Branham, Petitioner v. David Bergh, et al.; Rodney Branham, Petitioner v. Terry Malloy, et al. 559 U.S. 1047, 130 S. Ct. 2353, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 3042.

176 L. Ed. 2d 559,

April 5, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
